> Akka 用于构建高并发、分布式且具有容错机制的事件驱动型的应用，本文通过一个很简单的 project 来讲解 Akka 的一些基础知识。

## Akka Guide

Event-driven model: Actor perform work in response to messages. It's asynchronous.

Message should be immutable. Since they are shared between different threads.
